<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6 sm:py-8">
    <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
        Terms of Service & Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
        Please review these terms carefully before using Scatch services.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Last updated: March 4, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <aside class="lg:col-span-1 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
            Quick Navigation
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>
              <a href="#terms" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700"
                >Terms of Service</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700"
                >Privacy Policy</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700"
                >Contact for Policy Queries</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Important Summary
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Using Scatch means you agree to these terms.</li>
            <li>Your account information must stay accurate and secure.</li>
            <li>Payments are processed securely through approved gateways.</li>
            <li>Privacy requests can be raised through our contact page.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <section
          id="terms"
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"
        >
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 px-4 sm:px-6 py-4">
            <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Terms of Service
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div
            class="p-4 sm:p-6 space-y-5 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p>
              Welcome to
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">Scatch</span>. By
              accessing or using our website, you agree to comply with and be
              bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please
              discontinue use of the platform.
            </p>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                1. Account & Eligibility
              </h3>
              <p>
                You must provide accurate account details and maintain
                confidentiality of your login credentials. You are responsible
                for all activity performed through your account.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                2. Orders, Pricing & Availability
              </h3>
              <p>
                Product listings, offers, and pricing may change without prior
                notice. Orders are subject to confirmation, availability, and
                verification checks.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                3. Payments, Cancellations & Refunds
              </h3>
              <p>
                All payments are processed through secure payment partners.
                Cancellations and refunds are governed by applicable store
                policies and order status at the time of request.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                4. Prohibited Use
              </h3>
              <p>
                You agree not to misuse the platform, attempt unauthorized
                access, perform fraudulent transactions, or interfere with
                normal operation of the service.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                5. Limitation of Liability
              </h3>
              <p>
                To the maximum extent permitted by law, Scatch will not be
                liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
                arising from platform usage, delays, or service interruptions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section
          id="privacy"
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"
        >
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 px-4 sm:px-6 py-4">
            <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Privacy Policy
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div
            class="p-4 sm:p-6 space-y-5 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p>
              Scatch values your privacy and is committed to safeguarding your
              personal information. This section explains what data we collect,
              why we collect it, and how it is protected.
            </p>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                1. Information We Collect
              </h3>
              <p>
                We may collect name, contact details, shipping address, order
                history, payment metadata, and usage signals such as
                device/browser information.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                2. How We Use Information
              </h3>
              <p>
                Your data is used to process orders, deliver products, provide
                support, improve shopping experience, and communicate essential
                service updates.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                3. Data Sharing & Security
              </h3>
              <p>
                We share data only with trusted partners necessary for
                operations (payments, shipping, analytics), and we apply
                reasonable administrative and technical safeguards to protect
                your data.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                4. Cookies & Tracking
              </h3>
              <p>
                Cookies are used for session management, performance
                improvements, and personalized experience. You can manage cookie
                preferences through your browser settings.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                5. Your Rights
              </h3>
              <p>
                You may request access, correction, or deletion of personal
                information, subject to applicable legal and operational
                requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section
          id="contact"
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"
        >
          <div
            class="p-4 sm:p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4"
          >
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                Policy Questions
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                For any concerns related to terms or privacy, contact our
                support team.
              </p>
            </div>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition"
            >
              Contact Support
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
